title: Womens High Waisted Stretchy Jeans - Wide Leg, Baggy, Loose, Trendy Jeans for Women

Classic and Timeless: Our Womens Jeans are a wardrobe essential. With their classic design and quality construction, these jeans will never go out of style. They are perfect for any occasion, from a casual day to a night out at a party.
